Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(OP)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:04.50,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,ありがとうの言葉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.11,0:00:10.70,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,木漏れ日みたいで、いいね♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.27,0:00:25.76,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,空 雲 果てしない道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.34,0:00:31.09,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,ちっちゃい存在同士 手を取り
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.39,0:00:35.99,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,もっと 壮大 夢見てもいいかい？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.38,0:00:40.92,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,なんて 寛大な 地球だい？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.13,0:00:46.00,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,そう、きっと特別な双眼鏡だって、ね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.21,0:00:50.87,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,探した景色は見つからない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.20,0:00:55.50,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,世界で一番の絶景ポイントは
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.71,0:01:03.08,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,いつも目の前の“その笑顔”だったから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.28,0:01:08.16,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,ありがとう いつもとなりにいてくれて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.37,0:01:13.16,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,それだけでもう何もいらなかったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.34,0:01:19.08,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,なかなか素直に言えないこの気持ちあふれて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.15,0:01:24.64,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,今日もコハルビヨリだ いいね♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:04.50,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,一句「谢谢你」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.11,0:00:10.70,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,就像掠过树梢的阳光 赞♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.27,0:00:25.76,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝天 白云 漫漫长路
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.34,0:00:31.09,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,同样渺小的存在 只要手牵着手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.39,0:00:35.99,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,就能心怀更壮大的梦想？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.38,0:00:40.92,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,地球多么宽大
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.13,0:00:46.00,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 就算特制的望远镜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.21,0:00:50.87,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,也找不到心中的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.20,0:00:55.50,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,因为世界上最棒的景点
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.71,0:01:03.08,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,就是时刻绽放在眼前的那份笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.28,0:01:08.16,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你陪伴我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.37,0:01:13.16,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,有你相伴 别无所求
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.34,0:01:19.08,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,充满心中的这份心情 总是说不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.15,0:01:24.64,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也是暖和的小阳春 赞♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.97,0:01:29.68,staff,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)}翻译：dgwxx／其他：cunhan
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(main)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.68,0:01:39.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没钱？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.57,0:01:40.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.95,0:01:42.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次谷川岳倒是没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.13,0:01:45.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但今后可就…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.85,0:01:48.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,登山确实挺花钱的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.32,0:01:51.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去兼职不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.09,0:01:53.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兼职？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.91,0:01:55.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有时候也兼职的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.87,0:01:58.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小学生的家教？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.32,0:02:02.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看 这样分数的加法就好懂多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.19,0:02:05.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的 日向老师好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.36,0:02:09.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒是没打过工 不会很累吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.72,0:02:11.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实不轻松就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.40,0:02:15.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过只要能挣钱 就能做很多事情了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.38,0:02:22.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我用自己挣的钱买到防水冲锋衣的时候可高兴了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.42,0:02:26.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还在雨中到处跑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.01,0:02:28.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下雨还到处跑啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.49,0:02:35.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兼职虽然不容易 但能积累经验 一定会开阔视野的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.31,0:02:39.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但小葵没准做不来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.18,0:02:43.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又想用激将法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.69,0:02:44.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.66,0:02:45.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也太露骨了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.31,0:02:50.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 兼职什么的我也能做的！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.10,0:02:54.15,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(954,718)\bord1}我要兼职了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.72,0:02:53.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兼职？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.54,0:02:55.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挺好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.67,0:02:58.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过兼职可以 别耽误学习
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.80,0:02:59.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我努力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.51,0:03:02.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那想打什么工啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.45,0:03:05.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这就开始找…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.81,0:03:11.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 妈妈的朋友在开点心店
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.03,0:03:14.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个商业街的会长？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.62,0:03:18.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 铃叔之前说人手不够
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.94,0:03:19.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去打电话问问
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.49,0:03:22.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,认识的人更放心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.23,0:03:31.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 您好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.75,0:03:35.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是雪村家的女儿 叫小葵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.86,0:03:36.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久疏问候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.24,0:03:39.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢 小葵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.37,0:03:40.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有事嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.42,0:03:44.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 听妈妈说您那正在招兼职
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.48,0:03:47.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道您愿不愿意用我 打电话问一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.39,0:03:50.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那最好不过了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.45,0:03:52.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵这么可爱 当然欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.81,0:03:53.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.17,0:03:57.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天 等会能过来吗 两点左右
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.51,0:03:58.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神马！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.82,0:04:00.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太突然了 不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.47,0:04:03.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系没关系 当然能去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.31,0:04:05.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别忘带简历啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.99,0:04:06.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简历！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.81,0:04:12.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姓名 地址 动机…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.16,0:04:15.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的字好难看…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.66,0:04:17.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥 还剩一小时了！？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.72,0:04:20.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向 救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.77,0:04:24.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.96,0:04:28.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向！兼职的参加动机怎么写啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.67,0:04:33.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真兼职啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.92,0:04:36.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就写为爱好挣钱 不是挺好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.98,0:04:38.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉不好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.55,0:04:42.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要让对方认为你能认真工作就好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.26,0:04:44.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,证件照呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.12,0:04:46.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就去拍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.10,0:04:48.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拍的时候要微笑哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.48,0:04:51.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过小葵可不怎么会笑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.13,0:04:54.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.13,0:04:57.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵 面试的时候要微笑哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.39,0:05:02.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,措辞也很重要 但第一印象靠表情哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.75,0:05:05.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的笑容那么阴暗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.33,0:05:10.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笑容 笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.60,0:05:13.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真要上阵了确实难啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.56,0:05:16.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 按这个钮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.23,0:05:19.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要再拍一次吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.17,0:05:22.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是！刚刚的不算
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.58,0:05:33.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵 好久不见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.33,0:05:35.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说最近开始登山了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.69,0:05:37.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是健康的爱好 不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.31,0:05:39.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.37,0:05:40.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等下有空？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.10,0:05:43.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有空
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.76,0:05:48.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得去参加商业街联会 店里就剩一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.91,0:05:51.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能这就去帮帮她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.87,0:05:52.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.52,0:05:55.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,制服在里面的更衣室
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.95,0:05:57.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尺码不合适的话告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.07,0:06:01.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有不明白的就问店里的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.44,0:06:04.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 简历…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.32,0:06:05.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放在那边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.71,0:06:06.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那拜托啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.17,0:06:15.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头发是不是扎起来比较好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.52,0:06:22.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这打扮有些不好意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.80,0:06:25.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心里没着落
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.92,0:06:31.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 要这个 和这个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.75,0:06:36.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 我今后在这兼职 我叫雪村
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.41,0:06:38.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是小葵？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.03,0:06:40.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫小野塚光
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.41,0:06:41.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大学二年级
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.78,0:06:42.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫我小光哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.95,0:06:43.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.61,0:06:47.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.40,0:06:50.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵你好可爱噢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.42,0:06:52.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.88,0:06:54.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好随便的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.80,0:06:58.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我第一次做兼职 请多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.54,0:06:59.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简单得很
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.19,0:07:03.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之客人一进来 就大声问候「欢迎光临」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.05,0:07:05.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后问客人想要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.52,0:07:07.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重复一遍 收款
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.67,0:07:09.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 教你怎么用收银机
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.25,0:07:12.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.45,0:07:13.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.17,0:07:15.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好粗线条啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.53,0:07:16.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.36,0:07:19.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是坐办公室的工作比较适合我吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.87,0:07:20.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.16,0:07:23.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好闷！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.69,0:07:24.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.10,0:07:26.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是说这个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.27,0:07:27.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说话的时候要用底气！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.12,0:07:29.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.10,0:07:32.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK 没错就是这个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.83,0:07:34.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看 客人来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.73,0:07:36.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要大声问候哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.00,0:07:38.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.84,0:07:40.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不做也得做啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.45,0:07:47.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢 欢迎光临 您要点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.59,0:07:56.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 是 要苹果派和花饰蛋糕 还有芒果蛋糕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.37,0:07:57.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.58,0:08:00.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用着急 干活用心扎实
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.18,0:08:03.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.39,0:08:05.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.69,0:08:07.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扫码
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.96,0:08:11.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1,420日元
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.57,0:08:12.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.58,0:08:14.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收您2,000日元
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.00,0:08:20.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找您580日元
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.83,0:08:22.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.39,0:08:24.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵 看前面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.43,0:08:28.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笑容笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.06,0:08:35.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.32,0:08:37.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.35,0:08:38.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.14,0:08:40.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.50,0:08:41.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油噢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.51,0:08:42.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.64,0:08:44.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.43,0:08:45.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.72,0:08:48.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.27,0:08:50.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系 没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.03,0:08:52.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一开始很难为情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.23,0:08:56.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思直视对方的话 就看对方眼睛下方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.65,0:08:57.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之要面对客人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.38,0:08:59.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同时加上微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.63,0:09:04.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你自己是客人的话 店员微笑接待一定很高兴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.21,0:09:06.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.38,0:09:08.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.01,0:09:10.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是本店推荐噢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.05,0:09:12.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.18,0:09:14.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎再来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.06,0:09:18.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光姐 本来以为是个随随便便的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.28,0:09:19.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,工作可真实在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.26,0:09:21.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}好咯 久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.26,0:09:23.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,客人们购物也都很舒适
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.98,0:09:25.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,微笑噢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.61,0:09:26.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,微笑哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.51,0:09:31.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人看表情 表情改变印象
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.22,0:09:34.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 一定是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.15,0:09:36.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好！我也能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.01,0:09:41.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.39,0:09:43.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在呢在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.66,0:09:44.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.26,0:09:47.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.67,0:09:49.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛 我可是客人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.16,0:09:56.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去你家转转 结果说你已经来面试了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.10,0:10:00.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家店很好 我经常来买哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.72,0:10:02.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要这个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.95,0:10:05.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.18,0:10:08.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 小葵还会摆脸色啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.48,0:10:10.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您也是在这兼职的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.29,0:10:11.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.80,0:10:16.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫日向 小葵受您关照了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.00,0:10:21.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里哪里 小葵干得可好了 很不错哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.56,0:10:23.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊！好意外呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.98,0:10:27.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说日向 别耽误我干活了 快回去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.71,0:10:28.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.28,0:10:32.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我进来的时候 笑容很好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.54,0:10:34.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.82,0:10:43.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个破日向 罗哩叭嗦的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.81,0:10:48.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 仿佛心里轻松了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.97,0:10:51.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.32,0:10:53.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.08,0:10:58.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.78,0:11:01.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵今天很帮忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.53,0:11:02.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天再见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.30,0:11:05.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢两位
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.27,0:11:10.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呼 累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.63,0:11:11.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.55,0:11:13.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.24,0:11:16.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样 第一份兼职
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.59,0:11:23.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,累趴了 不过累得舒服 很有成就感呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.30,0:11:28.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 工作和登山很相似呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.66,0:11:32.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈不会是在这等我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.13,0:11:35.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有些担心呢 在家等不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.83,0:11:37.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.92,0:11:41.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子饿了吧 回家吃饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.85,0:11:47.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次兼职 不过几个小时
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.13,0:11:52.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我感到眼界开阔多了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.97,0:11:56.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然有些紧张 但心里很期待明天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.85,0:11:59.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待续
